graph TB
    User["User"]
    Cmd["/arckit.research Command"]
    Agent["arckit-research Agent<br/>(Task Tool Subprocess)"]
    WebSearch["WebSearch Tool"]
    Template["research-template.md"]
    Output["research/ARC-{PID}-RSCH-{NUM}-v{VER}.md"]
    Vendor["vendors/{vendor}-profile.md"]
    Tech["tech-notes/{topic}.md"]
    
    User -->|Invokes| Cmd
    Cmd -->|Delegates via Task| Agent
    Agent -->|Uses| WebSearch
    Agent -->|Reads| Template
    Agent -->|Writes| Output
    Agent -->|Spawns| Vendor
    Agent -->|Spawns| Tech
    
    subgraph "Context Isolation"
        Agent
        WebSearch
    end
